abstract: Wayne Rooney successfully plays with Manchester United under-21 team for over hour with no incident after missing 12 first-team matches due to knee injury; other soccer news noted.
lead_paragraph: Rooney emerged unscathed when he played just over an hour for Manchester United’s under-21 team after having missed 12 first-team matches with a knee injury.
